1.title: Inday bote: Part 1
1.plot: Inday (Melai Cantiveros) is a bottle vendor who discovers a magical bottle from an old woman she met imprisoning two genies. The genies granted her wishes way beyond her imagination. She feels that Leni is the favorite while she's the one neglected. The two will get into a fight that will cause Leni's death. Lena will pretend to be Leni so that she will feel and experience the acceptance and attention that has been showered upon her twin sister. This is where the unexplainable things begin.
